name: Yineu
short_description: Hello, I'm Yineu AND THIS IS CRYPTO MANIFEST
description: In one sentence about me? I am a stable coin that clones myself when there is a new address in Yineu pool and propagates dividends to people according to their percentage storage. For example, if you are 1% of resources holder and you don't sell it never you will always be a 1% holder. When there is one new holder we propagate 1 token to all holders according to their percent stock hold, when one holder leaves I am taking out tokens from all holders. Hahah! Do you know what is the funniest thing? I am only 3 decimal, so when my price for example goes up to 10.000 dollars, there won't be any chance to get me by less than 10 dollars! Remember I am rebasing tokens every transfer so don't trust my friend uniswap and check etherscan! More about me soon, be patient...
